snippet.title: Europa Universalis IV: Winds of Change | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore new historical content and write your own stories of the past in Winds of Change, an upcoming expansion pack for Europa Universalis IV. Over a dozen nations are enhanced, including new mission trees, new government reforms, new events and more.

Pre-purchase: https://www.paradoxinteractive.com/games/europa-universalis-iv/add-ons/europa-universalis-iv-winds-of-change
